quran[6{c,v,t}:
7,52,hum inn logon ke paas aik aisi kitaab le aeye hain jis ko hum ne ilm ki bana par mufasil banaya hai aur jo imaan laane walon ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat hai
7,53,"ab kya yeh log iss ke siwa kisi aur baat ke muntazir hain ke woh injaam samnay aa jaye jis ki yeh kitaab khabar day rahi hai? jis roz woh injaam samnay aa gaya wohi log jinhon ne usay nazar andaaz kar diya tha kahin ge ke"" waqai hamaray rab ke rasool haq le kar aeye thay, phir kya ab hamein kuch safarishi milein ge jo hamaray haq mein sifarish karen? ya hamein dobarah wapas hi bhaij diya jaye taakay jo kuch hum pehlay karte thay is ke bajaye ab dosray tareeqay par kaam kar ke deikhein"" unhon ne apne aap ko khasaray mein daal diya aur woh saaray jhoot jo unhon ne tasneef kar rakhay thay aaj un se gum ho gay"
7,54,"Dur haqeeqat tumhara rab Allah hi hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko chay dinon mein peda kya, phir apne takhat saltanat par jalva farma howa jo raat ko din par dhaank deta hai aur phir din raat ke peechay dora chala aata hai jis ne Sooraj aur chaand aur tarre peda kiye sab is ke farmaan ke tabay hain khabardaar raho! usi ki Khalq hai aur isi ka amar hai bara ba barket hai Allah , saaray jahanon ka maalik o parvar-digaar"
7,55,"a pannay rab ko poukaro girgrate hue aur chupkay chupkay, yaqeenan o hay hadd se guzarnay walon ko pasand nahi karta"
7,56,"zameen mein fasaad barpaa nah karo jabkay is ki islaah ho chuki hai aur khuda hi ko poukaro khauf ke sath aur tama ke sath, yaqeenan Allah ki rehmat naik kirdaar logon se qareeb hai"
7,57,"aur woh Allah hi hai jo hawaon ko apni rehmat ke agay agay khushkhabri liye hue bhejta hai, phir jab woh pani se lde hue baadal utha layte hain to inhen kisi murda sir zameen ki taraf harkat deta hai, aur wahan meen barsa kar ( usi meri hui zameen se ) terhan terhan ke phal nikaal lata hai dekho, is terhan hum mُrdon ko haalat mout se nikaltay hain, shayad ke tum is mushahiday se sabaq lau"
